flowchart TD
    REQ([Access Request]) --> PEP[Policy Enforcement Point]
    PEP --> COLLECT[Collect attributes]

    COLLECT --> SA[Subject Attributes\nuser.role, user.dept\nuser.clearance]
    COLLECT --> RA[Resource Attributes\ndoc.owner, doc.classification\ndoc.status]
    COLLECT --> AA[Action: read / write / delete]
    COLLECT --> EA[Environment Attributes\ntime.hour, request.ip\nmfa_verified]

    SA --> PDP[Policy Decision Point]
    RA --> PDP
    AA --> PDP
    EA --> PDP

    PDP --> PE[Evaluate applicable policies]
    PE --> RESULT{Decision}
    RESULT -- Permit --> ALLOW([Allow access to resource])
    RESULT -- Deny --> DENY([403 Forbidden])
    RESULT -- Not applicable --> DEFAULT{Default policy}
    DEFAULT -- Deny by default --> DENY
